thread.title: BRIEF-Corteva Agriscience And Monsanto Company Reach Licensing Agreement On Corn Insect Control Technology

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Corteva Agriscience And Monsanto Company Reach Licensing Agreement On Corn Insect Control Technology

organizations.name: monsanto company reach licensing agreement on corn insect control technology may 16

text:
May 16 (Reuters) - Monsanto Co:
* CORTEVA AGRISCIENCE™, AGRICULTURE DIVISION OF DOWDUPONT, AND MONSANTO COMPANY REACH LICENSING AGREEMENT ON NEXT-GENERATION CORN INSECT CONTROL TECHNOLOGY
* MONSANTO CO - FINANCIAL DETAILS OF AGREEMENT ARE NOT BEING DISCLOSED.
* MONSANTO CO - CORTEVA AGRISCIENCE TO GET LICENSE TO STACK CO’S CORN ROOTWORM III AND MON89034 TRAITS WITH CORTEVA AGRISCIENCE’S INSECT CONTROL TRAITS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
